title: Russia's Putin to meet Saudi defence minister on Sunday: Kremlin - Region - World
text: Related Russian air force hit 63 targets in Syria in past 24 hours: Military Russia accused over use of new cluster bombs in Syria Russia's Putin and Abu Dhabi crown prince to meet, discuss Syria: Kremlin Officials: CIA-backed Syrian rebels under Russian blitz Russian President Vladimir Putin will meet Saudi Defence Minister Mohammed bin Salman on the sidelines of the Russian Grand Prix in Sochi on Sunday, the Kremlin said.
